Housemates were left in high spirits last evening as Biggie entertained them to songs by their favourite artistes. What was simply seen as a request session by Teddy A to listen to some ‘Wizkid’ was granted by Biggie. Housemates took their turns in dancing to songs from their favourite artistes in front of the mirror. Ifu continued to thrill the house in an impressive display of twerking, accompanied by BamBam, as Teddy A continued to sing in the background. Read Also: BBNaija: Savagery, clapbacks define the course Alex came around, Tobi too. Lolu eventually had to leave Anto and Rico, Cee-C and Ahneeka joined in the fray.